{"tid":939900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超難受】加州賊仔爆格中餐館 被困通風管兩日全身沾滿油脂","createTime":"2018-12-13T13:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:08:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":102,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"d12b97620c4212e85ddfe4ff7dc4b65a2f84f224","tid":939900,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"美國加州一名疑似竊賊被困中餐館佈滿油脂的排氣口兩日。消防員趕到現場後，發現該名男子困在餐廳一個由廚房直達天台的金屬抽風口之中，花了半小時將他救出。<br />\n阿拉米達縣消防員周三接報到場後，聽到大樓內傳出呻吟聲，一查之下發現一名男子被困，將行動升級為救援任務，事後當局在facebook專頁寫道：「一名成年男性在消防員到達現場後30分鐘內，從通風系統中脫身。」<br />\n警方指這名男子年齡為29歲，他稱自己被困兩日。他獲救後體力衰弱以及出現脫水徵狀，由救護車送到醫院接受檢查，康復情況良好，目前正被當局扣留。警方同時循非法侵入和故意破壞方向調查案件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181213/large/1544671534_8077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544671534_8077.jpg&h=5c78563d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181213/large/1544671614_605d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544671614_605d.jpg&h=0b420f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181213/large/1544671724_c304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544671724_c304.jpg&h=33b78d93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4ea4fde3df58c792a792573b128116cbe0ab11e","tid":939900,"uid":19437,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"拉登派出恐怖分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a108116356b6d19c34362a93c567e44014f2773","tid":939900,"uid":38904,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"黑到以為係魷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\